---
title: One-Pot Plant-Based Mince Pilaf with Yoghurt & Crushed Peanuts
description: One-pot cooking isn’t just convenient, it’s also full of lots of lovely flavours as everything comes together. Take this delicious Plant-Based Mince Pilaf, the chermoula spices melt in the bowl. One irresistible and easy dinner coming right up!

